data.description: Price Improvement, Bring your offers!!! Priced for a quick sale & Ready for your personal touches. Plenty of potential w/this 4B/2b/2 Car Garage home on a spacious lot. NO HOA! On CITY WATER & SEWER! Home features great split floor plan w/large Master En-suite formal living & dinning space & large  eat in Kitchen, 2 guest bedrooms, Office/flex room & guest bath w/cabana door. Sizeable screened in porch & large fenced in back yard w/storage shed. Pick fruit from the trees in your own yard, including mango, starfruit &oranges! Wide driveway allows for multiple vehicles, boat, or RV. Close to shopping, grocery, parks, College campus, & main access roads, including Interstate 95. Only 1 hr to Orlando, 25 min to Vero Beach & 18 minutes to the BEACH! View rocket launches right from your yard!
